## Acceptance Criteria

### Functional
- [ ] Style struct with Option-wrapped fg, bg, attrs, underline_color
- [ ] Builder pattern: Style::new().fg().bg().bold().italic()...
- [ ] merge() cascades child over parent (child wins on conflict)
- [ ] patch() is symmetric with merge (parent.patch(child) == child.merge(parent))
- [ ] Attribute flags combine on merge (OR operation)
- [ ] is_empty() returns true when all fields are None
- [ ] has_attr() checks specific flags

### Type Properties
- [ ] #[derive(Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq, Hash)]
- [ ] const fn constructors where possible
- [ ] size_of::<Style>() <= 24 bytes

### Performance
- [ ] Style merge: < 50ns (branchless ops)
- [ ] Zero-cost when all fields are None
- [ ] No heap allocation in Style operations

### Logging
- [ ] trace! on merge operations

