   - Area offset (area.x, area.y)
   - Text scroll offset
   - Unicode character widths
3. **Cursor visibility**: May need to hide cursor for password fields or inactive states

## Important

This is the most critical category - broken cursor positioning makes inputs unusable.
Test thoroughly with real terminal interaction.

